comments: Abolished 1.4.1932 and added to the parish of Aston Bampton.

Created 1.4.1932 from the parishes of Aston & Cole and Chimney. 
    Abolished 1.4.1954 and added to the parish of Aston Bampton & Shifford

Created 1.4.1954 from the separate parishes of Aston Bampton and 
    Shifford.

Abolished 1.4.1971 and added to the parish of Carterton & 
    Black Bourton.
Abolished 25.12.1868 and added to the parish of Leafield.
Abolished 1.4.1932 and added to the parish of Standlake.

On 20.10.1844 a detached part of the parish of Broughton Poggs became 
    part of Gloucestershire; on 25.3.1886 this same area became part of the 
    parish of Lechlade, so that thereafter Broughton Poggs was again wholly in Oxfordshire. 
    Abolished 1.4.1954 and added to the parish of Filkins & Broughton Poggs. 
    See also Table 2, note (b).

Abolished 1.4.1954 and added to the parish of Burford & Upton 
    & Signet.

Created 1979 by renaming the parish of Burford & Upton & Signett. 
    See also Table 2, note (g).

Created 1.4.1954 from the parishes of Upton & SIgnet and Burford. 
    Renamed 1979 to become the parish of Burford.

Created 1.4.1971 out of the parishes of Black Bourton and Brize 
    Norton. See also Table 2, note (g).
Abolished 1.4.1932 and added to the parish of Aston Bampton.

Abolished 1.4.1932 and divided between the parishes of Witney, 
    Ducklington and South Leigh.
Abolished 25.3.1886 and added to the parish of Broadwell.

Created 26.3.1894 out of the parish of Broadwell. Abolished 1.4.1954 
    and added to the parish of Filkins & Broughton Poggs.

Created 1.4.1954 from the separate parishes of Filkins and Broughton 
    Poggs. See also Table 2, note (g).

Created 1.4.1948 out of the parish of Handborough. See also Table 
    2, note (g).

Abolished 1.4.1932 and divided between the parishes of Hardwick 
    with Yelford and Standlake.

Created 1.4.1932 out of the parishes of Hardwick, Standlake, Telford and Ducklington. See also Table 2, note 
    (g).

That part which until 1.4.1932 formed part of the parish of Asthal. 
    See also Table 2, note (c).
Abolished 1.4.1932 and added to the parish of North Leigh.

Abolished 1.4.1954 and added to the parish of Aston Bampton 
    & Shifford

The part in Berkshire was 
    transferred to Oxfordshire on 20.10.1844. 
    See also Table 2, note (g).
Abolished 25.12.1868 and added to the parish of Shilton.

Abolished 1.4.1932 and divided between the parishes of Swinbrook 
    & Widford, Shilton and Asthal.

Created 1.4.1932 from the parishes of Swinbrook, Widford, Fulbrook and Shilton. See also Table 2, note 
    (g).

Created 1894 from the rural part of the parish of Witney. Abolished 
    1.4.1898 and added to the parish of Witney.

Abolished 1.4.1954 and added to the parish of Burford & Upton 
    & Signet.

Transferred from Gloucstershire to Oxfordshire on 20.10.1844. 
    Abolished 1.4.1932 and divided between the parishes of Swinbrook & Widford and 
    Shilton.
Abolished 1.4.1932 and added to the parish of North Leigh.

Abolished 1.4.1932 and added to the parish of Hardwick with 
    Yelford.
